Renart Jewelry - Product Listing Application
Full-stack jewelry e-commerce application with real-time gold pricing and dynamic price calculation.
Live Demo
Application: https://renart-jewelry.vercel.app
Features
Backend:

RESTful API with Express.js
Dynamic pricing formula: Price = (popularityScore + 1) × weight × goldPrice
Real-time gold price integration from metals.live API
Advanced filtering system for price and popularity
Smart caching system (10-minute intervals)

Frontend:

Responsive carousel with touch/swipe support
Interactive color picker with 3 gold options (Yellow, White, Rose)
5-star rating system converted from popularity scores
Real-time filtering interface
Mobile-first responsive design
Typography compliance with PDF specifications

Technology Stack
Backend:

Node.js + Express.js
Axios for external API calls
CORS middleware
Railway deployment

Frontend:

React 18 with hooks
Tailwind CSS for styling
Lucide React for icons
Vercel deployment

External Services:

metals.live API for real-time gold pricing

API Endpoints

GET /api/products - List all products with dynamic pricing
GET /api/products?minPrice=100&maxPrice=500 - Filter by price range
GET /api/products?minPopularity=3&maxPopularity=5 - Filter by rating
GET /api/products/:id - Get single product details
GET /api/health - API health check

Design Specifications
Typography (PDF Compliant):

Main Title: Avenir Book 45px
Product Names: Avenir Book 14px
Product Prices: Avenir Book 14px
Color Labels: Avenir Book 12px
Star Ratings: Avenir Book 12px

Color Palette:

Yellow Gold: #E6CA97
White Gold: #D9D9D9
Rose Gold: #E1A4A9

Responsive Design

Desktop (1024px+): 4 products per view
Tablet (640-1024px): 2 products per view
Mobile (<640px): 1 product per view
Touch/swipe navigation on all devices

Installation & Development
Prerequisites:

Node.js 16+
Git

Setup:
bash# Clone repository
git clone https://github.com/baskann/renart-jewelry.git
cd renart-jewelry

# Backend setup
cd backend
npm install
npm run dev

# Frontend setup (new terminal)
cd frontend
npm install
npm start
Deployment

Backend: Railway.app
Frontend: Vercel.com
Environment Variable: REACT_APP_API_URL=https://renart-jewelry-production.up.railway.app

